sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant W as Wallet Service
    participant Orch as Transfer Orchestrator
    participant SA as Shard A (User A)
    participant SB as Shard B (User B)
    participant Ev as Event Stream

    Note over C,Ev: TRANSFER (cross-shard TCC)
    C->>W: POST /transfer (idempotency-key, A, B, amount)
    W->>W: validate + idempotency check
    W->>Orch: start transfer (transfer_id)

    alt same shard (fast path)
        Orch->>SA: BEGIN; debit A; credit B; ledger entries; COMMIT
        SA-->>Orch: ok
        Orch-)Ev: emit transfer event
        Orch-->>W: succeeded
        W-->>C: 200 {transfer_id, completed}
    else cross-shard (TCC)
        Note over Orch,SB: TRY phase — reserve on both shards
        Orch->>SA: reserve (A.reserved += amount, version check)
        alt A reserve fails (insufficient / conflict)
            SA--xOrch: failed
            Orch-->>W: failed
            W-->>C: 402 insufficient funds
        else A reserved
            SA-->>Orch: ok
            Orch->>SB: reserve (B.pending += amount)
            alt B reserve fails
                SB--xOrch: failed
                Note over Orch,SA: CANCEL — release A reservation
                Orch->>SA: release A.reserved
                SA-->>Orch: released
                Orch-->>W: failed
                W-->>C: 500 retryable
            else B reserved
                SB-->>Orch: ok

                Note over Orch,SB: CONFIRM — commit both shards
                Orch->>SA: confirm (reserved -> debit, append ledger)
                SA-->>Orch: committed
                Orch->>SB: confirm (pending -> credit, append ledger)
                alt B confirm fails
                    SB--xOrch: error
                    Note over Orch,SB: durable orchestrator retries (idempotent by transfer_id)
                    Orch->>SB: retry confirm
                    SB-->>Orch: committed
                else B confirm ok
                    SB-->>Orch: committed
                end

                Orch-)Ev: emit transfer events (audit, fraud, analytics)
                Orch-->>W: succeeded
                W-->>C: 200 {transfer_id, completed}
            end
        end
    end

    Note over SA,Ev: TTL backstop auto-cancels stuck reservations beyond lease
